# Popcorn chicken

## Jiao yan ( Chinese salt and pepper)

Toast Sichuan peppercorn, white peppercorn, and salt on a skillet. Then grind them in a blender.

- Sichuan peppercorn | 2 tbsp | 
- white pepper | 1 tbsp | 
- salt | 2 tbsp | 

## Marinate chicken

Dice chicken unit 2/3 inch cubes

- chicken | 500 g | 

Marinade with soy sauce, salt, five-spice powder, grated garlic, grated ginger, a few shakes of onion powder, all-purpose flour.

- soy sauce | 1 tbsp | 
- five-spice powder | 1 tsp | 
- garlic | 3 cloves | grated
- ginger | 1 tsp | grated
- onion powder | 1/2 tsp | 
- all-purpose flour | 2 tbsp | 
- salt | 1 1/4 tsp | 

Crack in 1 egg white then add fresh juice from 1/4 of an orange.

Mix until everything is well combined.

- egg | 1 | whites only
- orange | 1 | juiced

Cover it, let marinade for 15 minutes.

> Do not let it sit for too long or else the enzyme will over tenderize the meat.

